messages.subject: **Good Vibrations Registration Extended- NO Walk-Ins**
messages.msgSnippet: Based on several requests, I will be making some changes to the registration deadline for the Good Vibrations Unschooling Conference. Online Registration is
messages.messageBody:
Based on several requests, I will be making some changes to the registration deadline for the Good Vibrations Unschooling Conference.

Online Registration is still open and will remain open until Friday, August 14. The current May 1- Aug 1 prices still apply; there are no increases.

HOWEVER, this change means that there will be absolutely NO Walk-In
registrations. Please be registered by Aug 14- no exceptions- or you will not be admitted to the conference.

Thank you,

Flo Gascon
Conference Coordinator
http://goodvibrationsconference.com
